#!N  #!Rvpeomen VPE Options Menu #!N #!EC #!N #!N The  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   
Options #!EF menu allows you to customize tools and window features. 
#!N #!N The  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Options #!EF menu lists the following options: 
#!N #!I0 #!N #!N #!I0 #!N  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Tool Palettes #!EF #!I50 
#!N Toggles between displaying the tool palettes and not displaying them. 
You can also use the  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Ctrl+T #!EF accelerator key. #!N 
#!I0 #!N  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Control Panel Access... #!EF #!I50 #!N Allows you 
to specify which controls panels and control panel groups are accessible 
from the VPE. (See  #!Lcpa,dxall404 h Control Panel Access, Groups, and Hierarchies  #!EL  .) #!N #!I0 #!N  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Control 
Panel Groups... #!EF #!I50 #!N Displays a dialog box that allows 
you to create, modify and delete control panel groups. (See  #!Lcpa,dxall404 h Control Panel Access, Groups, and Hierarchies  #!EL  
.) #!N #!I0 #!N  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Grid ... #!EF #!I50 #!N Allows 
you to select the grid type you want to use on 
the canvas. A dialog box displays the choices. See  #!Lwindset,dxall353 h Customizing the VPE Window  #!EL  for 
more information about the  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Grid... #!EF option. #!I0 #!N #!N 
